                <h1>Duke football hosts Virginia Tech eyeing first crucial home win in five seasons</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/6b8ea494-fcdc-45e4-bfd3-4714bd85333b.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Duke&#x20;football&#x27;s&#x20;last&#x20;meaningful&#x20;home&#x20;win&#x20;came&#x20;in&#x20;2013.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Duke football's last meaningful home win came in 2013.</p>

